Qubits & 156 \\
Basis Gates & CS, Id, RX, RZ, RZZ, SX, X \\
CZ error (median) & $2.752\times 10^{-3}$ \\
SX error (median)& $2.705 \times10^{-4}$ \\
Readout Error (median) & $9.70 \times 10^{-3}$ \\ 
T$_1$ (median) & $137.23\, \mu s$ \\
